  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><dl><dd><i>For the tourney at Maidenpool in 103 AC, see <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_for_King_Viserys_I%27s_accession\" title=\"Tourney for King Viserys I&#39;s accession\">Tourney for King Viserys I's accession</a>.</i></dd></dl>\n<p>The <b>tourney at Maidenpool</b> was held at <a href=\"/index.php/Maidenpool\" title=\"Maidenpool\">Maidenpool</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_208_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">208&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Melee\">The Melee</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_at_Maidenpool&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Melee\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hardyng\" title=\"House Hardyng\"><img alt=\"House Hardyng.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/32px-House_Hardyng.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/48px-House_Hardyng.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/64px-House_Hardyng.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_Hardyng\" title=\"Humfrey Hardyng\">Humfrey Hardyng</a> won the melee.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Joust\">The Joust</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_at_Maidenpool&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Joust\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hardyng\" title=\"House Hardyng\"><img alt=\"House Hardyng.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/32px-House_Hardyng.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/48px-House_Hardyng.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/64px-House_Hardyng.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\"><img alt=\"Kingsguard.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/32px-Kingsguard.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/48px-Kingsguard.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/64px-Kingsguard.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_Hardyng\" title=\"Humfrey Hardyng\">Humfrey Hardyng</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Donnel_of_Duskendale\" title=\"Donnel of Duskendale\">Donnel of Duskendale</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hardyng\" title=\"House Hardyng\"><img alt=\"House Hardyng.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/32px-House_Hardyng.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/48px-House_Hardyng.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/64px-House_Hardyng.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\"><img alt=\"House Arryn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/32px-House_Arryn.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/48px-House_Arryn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/64px-House_Arryn.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_Hardyng\" title=\"Humfrey Hardyng\">Humfrey Hardyng</a> defeated Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Donnel_Arryn\" title=\"Donnel Arryn\">Donnel Arryn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hardyng\" title=\"House Hardyng\"><img alt=\"House Hardyng.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/32px-House_Hardyng.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/48px-House_Hardyng.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/64px-House_Hardyng.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Royce\" title=\"House Royce\"><img alt=\"House Royce.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cf/House_Royce.svg/32px-House_Royce.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cf/House_Royce.svg/48px-House_Royce.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cf/House_Royce.svg/64px-House_Royce.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_Hardyng\" title=\"Humfrey Hardyng\">Humfrey Hardyng</a> defeated Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Royce\" title=\"House Royce\">Royce</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_at_Maidenpool&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight\" title=\"The Hedge Knight\">The Hedge Knight</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403152452\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.038 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.084 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 148/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8786/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1111/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 9/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expa